      "description": "Hey there! You have got to see this beauty\u2014it's honestly like it just rolled off the showroom floor. I've babyed this car since day one, so there isn't a scratch on it and the interior still has that fresh smell! It drives like an absolute dream and has been kept in a climate-controlled garage. If you're looking for something that feels brand new without the brand-new price tag, this is definitely the one for you. Drop me a message if you want to come take a look!",
      "price": 44500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 16
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is a superlative example of the E46 M3, featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six power plant with individual throttle bodies. This unit is in concours-level condition, featuring documented rod bearing replacement and a reinforced rear subframe to ensure structural integrity. The high-revving, naturally aspirated engine delivers linear power through a crisp 6-speed Getrag manual transmission and a factory-spec M-variable limited-slip differential. The chassis remains exceptionally tight, with refreshed bushings and a suspension geometry that preserves the communicative steering and perfect 50/50 weight distribution this era is known for. This is a collector-grade vehicle for the discerning driver who demands mechanical perfection.",
      "price": 48900.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 16
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
