      "timestep_posted": 16
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional specimen that redefines the standard for pre-owned excellence. This vehicle has been fastidiously maintained in a climate-controlled environment, preserving its original showroom-floor luster. The exterior finish is breathtaking, free of any stone chips, door dings, or swirl marks, and has been treated with a multi-stage paint correction and professional-grade ceramic coating. Inside, the cabin remains in an untouched state; the premium leather upholstery retains its factory matte finish and supple texture, showing absolutely no bolster wear or creasing. Every electronic component, from the high-fidelity audio system to the navigation interface, operates flawlessly. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, with a comprehensive service history performed exclusively by master technicians using OEM parts. The engine bay is immaculate, reflecting a life of gentle use and rigorous upkeep. Included with the sale are all original manuals, two keys, and a thick folder of maintenance receipts. This is a rare opportunity to acquire a collector-quality vehicle that looks, smells, and drives as if it just rolled off the assembly line.",
      "price": 48500.0,
